import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    group_sizes = data.groupby('group').size()
    plt.hist(group_sizes, bins='auto', edgecolor='black')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.title("What is the distribution of group sizes?", wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    person_group_count = data.groupby('person')['group'].nunique()
    person_group_count.plot(kind='bar')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.title("Which person is in the most groups?", wrap=True)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    group_sizes = data.groupby('group').size()
    average_group_size = np.mean(group_sizes)
    
    plt.boxplot(group_sizes)
    plt.axhline(average_group_size, color='r', linestyle='--', label=f'Average: {average_group_size:.2f}')
    
    plt.xlabel('Groups')
    plt.ylabel('Number of People')
    plt.title('What is the average number of people in each group?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    people_count = data['person'].value_counts()
    people_not_in_group = people_count[people_count == 1]
    
    ax = people_not_in_group.plot(kind='bar')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.title("Are there any people who are not in any groups?", wrap=True)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
